name: Darkest Diffusion
description: This is a lightweight (2 vectors) embedding to mimic the art style of Darkest Dungeon with a vivid inked look. Trained on the base Stable Diffusion 1.5 model, but works decently with a variety of related models (example images are from several models to illustrate the different effects it can have).
